  description="A relaxing day trip to Chemka (Kikuletwa) Hot Springs, warm turquoise pools under ancient fig trees, perfect after a safari or Kilimanjaro climb."
  ogImage="https://gokilimanjarotreks.com/images/daytrip-chemka.jpg"
  ogImageAlt="Kikuletwa Hot Springs turquoise pools surrounded by fig trees"
  schemas={schemas}
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <img src="/images/daytrip-chemka.jpg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 40%;z-index:0;opacity:0.55" />
  <div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(100deg,rgba(2,6,14,0.88) 0%,rgba(2,6,14,0.82) 40%,rgba(2,6,14,0.55) 65%,rgba(2,6,14,0.15) 100%);z-index:1"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <span class="page-hero-eyebrow">Tanzania Day Trip</span>
    <h1>Chemka Hot Springs</h1>
    <p>Unwind in an enchanting desert oasis hidden within an arid scrubland plain. Chemka Hot Springs (also known as Kikuletwa) features beautiful pools of warm, crystal-clear turquoise water surrounded by a dense canopy of ancient fig trees and twisting roots. It is the perfect tropical paradise for swimming, relaxing, and refreshing your body after a dusty safari or a grueling mountain trek.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500" class="btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Nelson</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
    <p style="font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--amber-cta);font-weight:700;margin:30px 0 18px">From $85 per person</p>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Highlights</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left:22px;margin-bottom:8px">
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Swim in perfectly clear, warm geothermal water pools.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Play around on the rope swings or enjoy a natural &#39;fish pedicure&#39; from tiny river fish.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Relax in a striking, lush jungle oasis tucked away inside a dry savannah landscape.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">A Day on This Trip</h2>
    <ol style="padding-left:22px;margin-bottom:8px">
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">09:00 AM: Depart Arusha or Moshi, driving past sugar cane plantations and baobab patches down bumpy dirt roads.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">10:30 AM: Arrive at the springs; change into swimwear and dive into the inviting, warm turquoise water.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">01:00 PM: Enjoy a freshly cooked hot lunch featuring local favorites like Chipsi Mayai or Nyama Choma.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">02:00 PM: Spend the afternoon lounging on the banks, sunbathing, or enjoying the rope swings.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">04:00 PM: Pack up and drive back to town as the sun begins to set.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">What is Included</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Round-trip transport, hot springs entry fees, local guide, freshly prepared local lunch, and bottled water.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">What is Not Included</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Swimwear rentals (best to bring your own), alcoholic drinks, and tips.</p>
    <p style="font-size:.92rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-top:18px">Every day trip is private and fully customisable. Prices vary with group size and season, so message Nelson for an exact quote for your dates.</p>
  </div>
</section>

